  "detailed_description": "<h1>Let´s Chat on Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the world of this unique fantasy game and take the chance to find out why we play. You will fight tactical battles, all one-of-a-kind, with loads of different creatures to fight and play. All this happens in a welcoming, warm and beautiful world.     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your creatures and their abilities wisely for victory!    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674140/extras/98e60ce0bfef22daa4c35dc4d9fc40f1.poster.avif?t=1736185099\" width=600 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674140/extras/98e60ce0bfef22daa4c35dc4d9fc40f1.webm?t=1736185099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674140/extras/98e60ce0bfef22daa4c35dc4d9fc40f1.mp4?t=1736185099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are six classes of creatures. For every battle you need to choose different classes and creatures. If a game with a short but meaningful story, where every battle and character holds a new surprise for you sounds intriguing, A Game´s Tale is the right choice. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674140/extras/02ec001489d86efe4f23efc37ffb1665.poster.avif?t=1736185099\" width=600 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674140/extras/02ec001489d86efe4f23efc37ffb1665.webm?t=1736185099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674140/extras/02ec001489d86efe4f23efc37ffb1665.mp4?t=1736185099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With every victory you grow your deck! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674140/extras/04e2123cbaa8b5f2c743f2efe974ae01.avif?t=1736185099\" width=600 height=600 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the world of this unique fantasy game and take the chance to find out why we play. You will fight tactical battles, all one-of-a-kind, with loads of different creatures to fight and play. All this happens in a welcoming, warm and beautiful world.     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your creatures and their abilities wisely for victory!    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674140/extras/98e60ce0bfef22daa4c35dc4d9fc40f1.poster.avif?t=1736185099\" width=600 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674140/extras/98e60ce0bfef22daa4c35dc4d9fc40f1.webm?t=1736185099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674140/extras/98e60ce0bfef22daa4c35dc4d9fc40f1.mp4?t=1736185099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are six classes of creatures. For every battle you need to choose different classes and creatures. If a game with a short but meaningful story, where every battle and character holds a new surprise for you sounds intriguing, A Game´s Tale is the right choice. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674140/extras/02ec001489d86efe4f23efc37ffb1665.poster.avif?t=1736185099\" width=600 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674140/extras/02ec001489d86efe4f23efc37ffb1665.webm?t=1736185099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674140/extras/02ec001489d86efe4f23efc37ffb1665.mp4?t=1736185099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With every victory you grow your deck! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2674140/extras/04e2123cbaa8b5f2c743f2efe974ae01.avif?t=1736185099\" width=600 height=600 /></span></p>",
